tool_description: SQUAKE helps businesses to build sustainable products! With the most performant API in the market, we help travel, mobility, and logistics companies calculate carbon emissions and purchase certified climate contributions in real-time. Implemented within mins!
title: SQUAKE

api_list.name: Purchase
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://squake.p.rapidapi.com/carbon_activities/ENTER_CARBON_ACTIVITY_ID_HERE/purchase"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "squake.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.put(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
